Dialogue: 0.0:03:09.62.0:03:10.81.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(317.371)}- Jerry!
Dialogue: 0.0:03:09.62.0:03:10.81.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(320.410)}- Beth!
Dialogue: 0.0:03:10.89.0:03:11.91.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(281.371)}Oh. my God.
Dialogue: 0.0:03:10.89.0:03:11.91.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(213.413)}My parents are so loud.
Dialogue: 0.0:03:11.99.0:03:12.98.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(282.410)}I want to die.
Dialogue: 0.0:03:13.06.0:03:14.39.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an5\pos(359.70)}Mm. there is
Dialogue: 0.0:03:13.06.0:03:14.39.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an5\pos(358.112)}no God. Summer.
Dialogue: 0.0:03:14.46.0:03:16.22.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an5\pos(360.71)}You got to rip that band-aid off
Dialogue: 0.0:03:14.46.0:03:16.22.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an5\pos(357.110)}now. You'll thank me later.
Dialogue: 0.0:03:16.29.0:03:18.09.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(193.371)}Okay. with all due respect.
Dialogue: 0.0:03:16.29.0:03:18.09.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(322.410)}Rick --
Dialogue: 0.0:03:18.16.0:03:20.03.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an5\pos(357.71)}What am I talking about?
Dialogue: 0.0:03:18.16.0:03:20.03.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an5\pos(357.113)}What respect is due?
Dialogue: 0.0:03:20.10.0:03:23.66.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an5\pos(358.71)}How is my son supposed to pass
Dialogue: 0.0:03:20.10.0:03:23.66.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an5\pos(358.113)}his classes if you keep dragging
Dialogue: 0.0:03:23.73.0:03:26.36.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an5\pos(359.71)}him off for high-concept
Dialogue: 0.0:03:23.73.0:03:26.36.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an5\pos(357.113)}sci-fi rigmarole?
Dialogue: 0.0:03:26.44.0:03:28.77.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an5\pos(359.71)}Listen. Jerry. I-I don't want to
Dialogue: 0.0:03:26.44.0:03:28.77.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an5\pos(356.113)}overstep my bounds or anything.
Dialogue: 0.0:03:28.84.0:03:30.40.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(266.371)}It's your house.
Dialogue: 0.0:03:28.84.0:03:30.40.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(272.413)}It's your world.
Dialogue: 0.0:03:30.47.0:03:31.53.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(184.410)}You're a real Julius Caesar.
Dialogue: 0.0:03:31.61.0:03:32.70.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(226.371)}But I'll tell you some--
Dialogue: 0.0:03:31.61.0:03:32.70.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(271.413)}tell you how --
Dialogue: 0.0:03:32.77.0:03:33.94.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(261.368)}how I feel about
Dialogue: 0.0:03:32.77.0:03:33.94.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(276.413)}school. Jerry.
Dialogue: 0.0:03:34.01.0:03:35.27.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(231.410)}It's a waste of time --
Dialogue: 0.0:03:35.34.0:03:36.68.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(245.371)}A bunch of people
Dialogue: 0.0:03:35.34.0:03:36.68.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(261.413)}running around.
Dialogue: 0.0:03:36.75.0:03:37.80.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(204.413)}bumping into each other.
Dialogue: 0.0:03:37.88.0:03:39.58.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(233.371)}G-guy up front says.
Dialogue: 0.0:03:37.88.0:03:39.58.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(264.413)}"Two plus two."
Dialogue: 0.0:03:39.65.0:03:41.38.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(249.371)}The people in the
Dialogue: 0.0:03:39.65.0:03:41.38.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(254.413)}back say. "Four."
Dialogue: 0.0:03:41.45.0:03:43.58.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(179.371)}Then the bell rings. and they
Dialogue: 0.0:03:41.45.0:03:43.58.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(206.413)}give you a carton of milk
Dialogue: 0.0:03:43.65.0:03:46.78.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(114.371)}and a piece of paper that says you can
Dialogue: 0.0:03:43.65.0:03:46.78.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(171.413)}go take a dump or something.
Dialogue: 0.0:03:46.86.0:03:49.29.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(224.370)}I mean. it's -- it's not a
Dialogue: 0.0:03:46.86.0:03:49.29.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(176.413)}place for smart people. Jerry.
Dialogue: 0.0:03:49.36.0:03:50.48.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(227.368)}And I know that's not
Dialogue: 0.0:03:49.36.0:03:50.48.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(247.413)}a popular opinion.
Dialogue: 0.0:03:50.56.0:03:53.69.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(233.371)}but it's my two cents
Dialogue: 0.0:03:50.56.0:03:53.69.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(280.410)}on the issue.
Dialogue: 0.0:03:53.76.0:03:55.39.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(189.371)}This was a good breakfast.
Dialogue: 0.0:03:53.76.0:03:55.39.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(330.410)}Beth.
Dialogue: 0.0:03:55.46.0:03:57.52.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(233.371)}You really made the
Dialogue: 0.0:03:55.46.0:03:57.52.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(215.413)}crap out of those eggs.
Dialogue: 0.0:03:57.60.0:03:59.86.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(246.371)}I wish your mother
Dialogue: 0.0:03:57.60.0:03:59.86.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(222.410)}was here to eat them.
Dialogue: 0.0:03:59.94.0:04:01.20.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(305.412)}Oh. Dad.
Dialogue: 0.0:04:01.27.0:04:02.10.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(319.410)}What?
Dialogue: 0.0:04:02.17.0:04:04.07.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(306.410)}For real?
Dialogue: 0.0:04:04.14.0:04:05.80.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(288.368)}TEACHER:
Dialogue: 0.0:04:04.14.0:04:05.80.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(129.413)}All right. now. everybody get settled.
Dialogue: 0.0:04:05.87.0:04:07.54.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(181.413)}Get away from the windows!
Dialogue: 0.0:04:07.61.0:04:08.80.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(194.413)}Now. look. we're gonna be
Dialogue: 0.0:04:08.88.0:04:10.78.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(218.371)}dealing with some real
Dialogue: 0.0:04:08.88.0:04:10.78.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(240.413)}serious stuff today.
Dialogue: 0.0:04:10.85.0:04:12.75.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(189.371)}You might have heard of it.
Dialogue: 0.0:04:10.85.0:04:12.75.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(264.410)}It's called math.
Dialogue: 0.0:04:12.81.0:04:14.87.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(270.370)}And without it.
Dialogue: 0.0:04:12.81.0:04:14.87.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(181.412)}none of us would even exist.
Dialogue: 0.0:04:14.95.0:04:17.08.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(221.371)}so let's jump right in --
Dialogue: 0.0:04:14.95.0:04:17.08.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(277.413)}two plus two.
Dialogue: 0.0:04:17.15.0:04:18.14.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(310.410)}Jessica.
Dialogue: 0.0:04:18.22.0:04:19.62.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(276.413)}Five plus five.
Dialogue: 0.0:04:19.69.0:04:20.92.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(299.410)}Tenssica.
Dialogue: 0.0:04:20.99.0:04:21.92.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(285.413)}Okay. good.
Dialogue: 0.0:04:21.99.0:04:23.08.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(235.413)}It's time for the quiz.
Dialogue: 0.0:04:23.16.0:04:24.15.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(291.413)}[all groan ]
Dialogue: 0.0:04:24.23.0:04:25.46.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(211.371)}Yeah. you know what?!
Dialogue: 0.0:04:24.23.0:04:25.46.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(281.412)}Aw. too bad!
Dialogue: 0.0:04:25.53.0:04:26.59.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(316.413)}Tough!
Dialogue: 0.0:04:26.66.0:04:28.82.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(241.370)}First row. take one.
Dialogue: 0.0:04:26.66.0:04:28.82.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(237.410)}Pass it back for me.
Dialogue: 0.0:04:28.90.0:04:30.70.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(234.371)}The stakes are high
Dialogue: 0.0:04:28.90.0:04:30.70.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(284.410)}in this room.
Dialogue: 0.0:04:30.77.0:04:34.07.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(225.371)}There's crucial things
Dialogue: 0.0:04:30.77.0:04:34.07.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(192.413)}happening here every day.
Dialogue: 0.0:04:34.14.0:04:35.00.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(214.413)}People getting smarter.
Dialogue: 0.0:04:35.07.0:04:36.13.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(177.413)}Some of y'all getting dumber.
Dialogue: 0.0:04:36.20.0:04:38.44.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(251.371)}Some of y'all ain't
Dialogue: 0.0:04:36.20.0:04:38.44.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(258.413)}gonna see 3:00.
Dialogue: 0.0:04:40.24.0:04:41.97.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(298.368)}JESSICA:
Dialogue: 0.0:04:40.24.0:04:41.97.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(302.413)}Hi. Morty.
Dialogue: 0.0:04:42.04.0:04:43.03.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(319.410)}Whoa!
Dialogue: 0.0:04:43.11.0:04:44.17.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(290.412)}Hi. Jessica.
Dialogue: 0.0:04:44.25.0:04:45.58.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(200.413)}Can I show these to you?
Dialogue: 0.0:04:45.65.0:04:46.55.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(325.410)}Wow.
Dialogue: 0.0:04:46.62.0:04:47.71.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(223.413)}Th-they're both great.
Dialogue: 0.0:04:47.78.0:04:48.72.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(289.413)}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0.0:04:48.78.0:04:49.77.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(159.410)}You know what I named these?
Dialogue: 0.0:04:49.85.0:04:51.08.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(260.413)}My little Morties.
Dialogue: 0.0:04:51.15.0:04:53.95.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(228.371)}Uh. that's flattering...
Dialogue: 0.0:04:51.15.0:04:53.95.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(254.410)}and a little weird.
Dialogue: 0.0:04:54.02.0:04:55.99.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(204.371)}Do you know what I want
Dialogue: 0.0:04:54.02.0:04:55.99.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(227.413)}you to do with them?
Dialogue: 0.0:04:56.06.0:04:57.03.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(265.410)}Rename them?
Dialogue: 0.0:04:57.09.0:04:58.49.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(266.413)}Squeeze them.
Dialogue: 0.0:04:58.56.0:04:59.65.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(252.410)}Manhandle them.
Dialogue: 0.0:04:59.73.0:05:00.75.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(208.410)}Give them the business.
Dialogue: 0.0:05:00.83.0:05:02.23.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(185.413)}See if you can shuffle them.
Dialogue: 0.0:05:02.30.0:05:04.53.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(201.371)}I mean. really get in there
Dialogue: 0.0:05:02.30.0:05:04.53.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(207.410)}and knock them around.
Dialogue: 0.0:05:04.60.0:05:05.76.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(240.413)}No wrong answers.
Dialogue: 0.0:05:05.83.0:05:06.67.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(325.410)}Wow.
Dialogue: 0.0:05:06.74.0:05:08.07.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(234.413)}Well. okay. Jessica.
Dialogue: 0.0:05:08.14.0:05:09.47.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(222.413)}L-let's give this a shot.
Dialogue: 0.0:05:09.54.0:05:10.73.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(336.410)}Mm.
Dialogue: 0.0:05:10.81.0:05:11.83.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(295.413)}Oh. Morty.
Dialogue: 0.0:05:11.91.0:05:13.38.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(187.413)}What are you doing to me?
Dialogue: 0.0:05:13.44.0:05:15.60.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(284.371)}Uh. I-I'm just
Dialogue: 0.0:05:13.44.0:05:15.60.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(268.413)}doing my best.
Dialogue: 0.0:05:15.68.0:05:16.67.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(324.413)}Morty!
Dialogue: 0.0:05:16.75.0:05:17.58.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(183.413)}What are you doing to me?!
Dialogue: 0.0:05:17.65.0:05:18.48.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(310.410)}Jessica.
Dialogue: 0.0:05:18.55.0:05:19.64.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(324.413)}Morty!
Dialogue: 0.0:05:19.71.0:05:21.71.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(284.371)}[ mumbling ]
Dialogue: 0.0:05:19.71.0:05:21.71.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(310.410)}Jessica.
Dialogue: 0.0:05:21.78.0:05:23.75.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(198.370)}Five more minutes of this.
Dialogue: 0.0:05:21.78.0:05:23.75.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(210.413)}and I'm gonna get mad.
Dialogue: 0.0:05:23.82.0:05:25.72.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(290.410)}Je-Jessica.
Dialogue: 0.0:05:25.79.0:05:27.02.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(284.371)}[ mumbling ]
Dialogue: 0.0:05:25.79.0:05:27.02.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(310.410)}Jessica.
Dialogue: 0.0:05:27.09.0:05:28.25.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(287.371)}Not my fault
Dialogue: 0.0:05:27.09.0:05:28.25.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(249.413)}this is happening.
Dialogue: 0.0:05:28.32.0:05:30.59.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(243.413)}[school bell rings]
Dialogue: 0.0:05:30.66.0:05:32.36.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(263.412)}Well. well. well.
Dialogue: 0.0:05:32.43.0:05:33.36.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(236.413)}Uh. morning. Frank.
Dialogue: 0.0:05:33.43.0:05:34.52.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(292.413)}"Morning"?
Dialogue: 0.0:05:34.60.0:05:35.53.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(235.368)}What was -- what is
Dialogue: 0.0:05:34.60.0:05:35.53.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(206.413)}that supposed to mean?
Dialogue: 0.0:05:35.60.0:05:36.72.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(213.413)}You making fun of me?
Dialogue: 0.0:05:36.80.0:05:37.93.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(256.371)}Are you trying to
Dialogue: 0.0:05:36.80.0:05:37.93.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(224.413)}say my family's poor?
Dialogue: 0.0:05:38.00.0:05:39.09.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(255.413)}Oh. geez. Frank.
Dialogue: 0.0:05:39.17.0:05:40.47.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(264.368)}I don't know if a
Dialogue: 0.0:05:39.17.0:05:40.47.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(244.413)}knife is necessary.
Dialogue: 0.0:05:40.54.0:05:42.90.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(161.371)}I mean. you know. y-you kind of
Dialogue: 0.0:05:40.54.0:05:42.90.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(176.413)}had things handled without it.
Dialogue: 0.0:05:42.97.0:05:45.24.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(269.371)}You telling me
Dialogue: 0.0:05:42.97.0:05:45.24.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(248.413)}how to bully now?
Dialogue: 0.0:05:45.31.0:05:46.71.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(241.413)}Big mistake. Morty.
Dialogue: 0.0:05:46.78.0:05:51.04.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(183.371)}And now I'm gonna cut you.
Dialogue: 0.0:05:46.78.0:05:51.04.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(214.413)}'cause my family's rich.
Dialogue: 0.0:05:51.11.0:05:52.58.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(308.413)}[gasps]
Dialogue: 0.0:05:52.65.0:05:54.01.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(223.413)}There you are. Morty.
Dialogue: 0.0:05:54.08.0:05:55.24.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(281.410)}Listen to me.
Dialogue: 0.0:05:55.32.0:05:56.98.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(202.371)}I got an errand to run in a
Dialogue: 0.0:05:55.32.0:05:56.98.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(193.410)}whole different dimension.
Dialogue: 0.0:05:57.05.0:05:58.52.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(176.413)}I need an extra pair of hands.
Dialogue: 0.0:05:58.59.0:05:59.75.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(264.413)}Oh. geez. Rick.
Dialogue: 0.0:05:59.82.0:06:01.19.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(189.413)}W-what'd you do to Frank?
Dialogue: 0.0:06:01.26.0:06:02.62.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(204.371)}It's pretty obvious. Morty.
Dialogue: 0.0:06:01.26.0:06:02.62.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(292.410)}I froze him.
Dialogue: 0.0:06:02.69.0:06:04.56.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(284.368)}Now listen --
Dialogue: 0.0:06:02.69.0:06:04.56.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(212.413)}I need your help. Morty.
Dialogue: 0.0:06:04.63.0:06:06.19.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(256.371)}I mean. we got --
Dialogue: 0.0:06:04.63.0:06:06.19.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(265.413)}we got to get --
