Dialogue: 0.0:09:05.57.0:09:07.41.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(234.413)}why I want to leave.
Dialogue: 0.0:09:07.48.0:09:08.34.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(256.410)}Ta-ta-ta-ta-ta-ta.
Dialogue: 0.0:09:08.41.0:09:11.51.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(234.413)}Morty. you see this?
Dialogue: 0.0:09:11.58.0:09:13.55.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(225.371)}You see what we just
