Dialogue: 0.0:09:14.85.0:09:15.94.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(252.413)}The Mega trees?
Dialogue: 0.0:09:16.02.0:09:17.35.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(232.371)}That's right. Morty --
Dialogue: 0.0:09:16.02.0:09:17.35.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(265.413)}the Mega trees
Dialogue: 0.0:09:17.42.0:09:18.72.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(183.413)}with the Mega fruit on them.
Dialogue: 0.0:09:18.79.0:09:20.22.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(240.368)}And that's what I'm
