Dialogue: 0.0:09:20.29.0:09:21.65.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(184.413)}That's where my seeds are.
Dialogue: 0.0:09:21.72.0:09:22.78.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(220.368)}If we would have done
Dialogue: 0.0:09:21.72.0:09:22.78.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(249.413)}what you wanted.
Dialogue: 0.0:09:22.86.0:09:24.12.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(242.368)}I would have never
Dialogue: 0.0:09:22.86.0:09:24.12.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(251.412)}have found them.
Dialogue: 0.0:09:24.19.0:09:25.85.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(186.371)}because y-- because you're
Dialogue: 0.0:09:24.19.0:09:25.85.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(222.410)}so in love with school.
Dialogue: 0.0:09:25.93.0:09:27.23.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(254.413)}All right. all right.
Dialogue: 0.0:09:27.30.0:09:29.13.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(189.371)}So. what's so special about
Dialogue: 0.0:09:27.30.0:09:29.13.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(211.413)}these seeds. anyways?
Dialogue: 0.0:09:29.20.0:09:30.86.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(261.368)}You ask a lot of
Dialogue: 0.0:09:29.20.0:09:30.86.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(252.413)}questions. Morty.
Dialogue: 0.0:09:30.93.0:09:32.23.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(229.413)}Not very charismatic.
Dialogue: 0.0:09:32.30.0:09:33.67.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(236.371)}It makes you kind of
Dialogue: 0.0:09:32.30.0:09:33.67.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(247.413)}an [burps] under--
Dialogue: 0.0:09:33.74.0:09:35.17.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(209.413)}[burps] underfoot figure.
Dialogue: 0.0:09:35.24.0:09:36.43.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(174.413)}Just take these shoes. Morty.
Dialogue: 0.0:09:36.50.0:09:38.27.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(236.371)}They're sp-- [burps]
Dialogue: 0.0:09:36.50.0:09:38.27.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(207.413)}special grappling shoes.
Dialogue: 0.0:09:38.34.0:09:40.57.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(187.371)}When you're wearing these
Dialogue: 0.0:09:38.34.0:09:40.57.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(189.413)}things -- ba-- these babies.
Dialogue: 0.0:09:40.64.0:09:43.31.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(171.371)}you can basically just walk on
Dialogue: 0.0:09:40.64.0:09:43.31.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(168.413)}any surface you want. Morty --
Dialogue: 0.0:09:43.38.0:09:45.35.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(255.371)}up. down. below.
Dialogue: 0.0:09:43.38.0:09:45.35.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(219.410)}turn around to the left.
Dialogue: 0.0:09:45.41.0:09:47.25.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(203.371)}These things really bring
Dialogue: 0.0:09:45.41.0:09:47.25.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(276.413)}it all together.
