Dialogue: 0.0:09:51.22.0:09:52.48.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(259.410)}to be turned on!
Dialogue: 0.0:09:52.55.0:09:55.35.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(322.368)}BETH:
Dialogue: 0.0:09:52.55.0:09:55.35.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(129.413)}I am not putting my father in a home!
Dialogue: 0.0:09:55.42.0:09:57.29.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(245.371)}He just came back
Dialogue: 0.0:09:55.42.0:09:57.29.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(290.413)}into my life.
Dialogue: 0.0:09:57.36.0:10:00.76.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(172.371)}and you want to grab him and
Dialogue: 0.0:09:57.36.0:10:00.76.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(170.410)}stuff him under a mattress like
Dialogue: 0.0:10:00.83.0:10:02.32.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(171.410)}last month's Victoria's Secret?
Dialogue: 0.0:10:02.40.0:10:04.87.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(170.371)}I told you -- I was ordering you
