Dialogue: 0.0:10:04.93.0:10:09.60.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(165.371)}More importantly. your father is
Dialogue: 0.0:10:04.93.0:10:09.60.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(164.410)}a horrible influence on our son.
Dialogue: 0.0:10:09.67.0:10:10.97.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(172.413)}Everything cool in here. Beth?
Dialogue: 0.0:10:11.04.0:10:11.87.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(270.412)}It's fine. Davin.
Dialogue: 0.0:10:11.94.0:10:13.00.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(291.413)}Okay. cool.
Dialogue: 0.0:10:13.07.0:10:14.51.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(247.370)}You know. we did
Dialogue: 0.0:10:13.07.0:10:14.51.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(215.413)}something great today.
Dialogue: 0.0:10:14.58.0:10:18.07.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(157.371)}There's nothing more noble and
Dialogue: 0.0:10:14.58.0:10:18.07.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(172.410)}free than the heart of a horse.
Dialogue: 0.0:10:18.15.0:10:20.58.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(234.371)}Since we're fighting.
Dialogue: 0.0:10:18.15.0:10:20.58.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(205.413)}if you ever have an affair
Dialogue: 0.0:10:20.65.0:10:22.17.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(243.371)}with that guy. I will
Dialogue: 0.0:10:20.65.0:10:22.17.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(214.410)}come to the hotel room
Dialogue: 0.0:10:22.25.0:10:24.72.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(214.371)}and blow my brains out
Dialogue: 0.0:10:22.25.0:10:24.72.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(190.413)}all over your naked bodies.
Dialogue: 0.0:10:24.79.0:10:27.76.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(225.371)}Look. I appreciate the
Dialogue: 0.0:10:24.79.0:10:27.76.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(212.413)}stress you're under. but
Dialogue: 0.0:10:27.82.0:10:30.16.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(188.371)}Morty was having trouble in
Dialogue: 0.0:10:27.82.0:10:30.16.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(147.413)}school way before my dad moved
Dialogue: 0.0:10:30.23.0:10:33.53.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(195.371)}in. and the only influence I
Dialogue: 0.0:10:30.23.0:10:33.53.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(186.413)}can see Rick having is that.
Dialogue: 0.0:10:33.60.0:10:36.72.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(198.370)}for the first time in his life.
Dialogue: 0.0:10:33.60.0:10:36.72.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(244.413)}Morty has a friend.
