Dialogue: 0.0:10:42.94.0:10:43.87.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(206.413)}I'm my father's daughter.
Dialogue: 0.0:10:43.94.0:10:44.93.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(301.410)}I'm smart.
Dialogue: 0.0:10:45.01.0:10:45.91.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(250.371)}Why do you think
Dialogue: 0.0:10:45.01.0:10:45.91.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(232.413)}I'm a heart surgeon?
Dialogue: 0.0:10:45.97.0:10:46.81.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(228.413)}Horse heart surgeon.
