Dialogue: 0.0:10:49.94.0:10:51.67.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(183.413)}father might be able to have
Dialogue: 0.0:10:51.75.0:10:52.87.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(269.368)}a chat with me
Dialogue: 0.0:10:51.75.0:10:52.87.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(265.410)}this afternoon?
Dialogue: 0.0:10:52.95.0:10:55.61.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(191.413)}[suspenseful music plays]
Dialogue: 0.0:10:55.68.0:10:58.15.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(186.371)}Morty. oh. you really d-did a
