Dialogue: 0.0:10:59.45.0:11:00.65.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(201.413)}turn the shoes on. Morty.
Dialogue: 0.0:11:00.72.0:11:01.92.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(254.410)}for them to work.
Dialogue: 0.0:11:01.99.0:11:03.15.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(279.370)}Yeah. look --
Dialogue: 0.0:11:01.99.0:11:03.15.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(256.410)}I turned mine on.
Dialogue: 0.0:11:03.22.0:11:04.49.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(256.371)}I had no problem
Dialogue: 0.0:11:03.22.0:11:04.49.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(243.413)}getting down here.
