Dialogue: 0.0:11:06.13.0:11:07.39.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(211.413)}I'm in a lot of pain. Rick.
Dialogue: 0.0:11:07.46.0:11:08.90.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(229.412)}Yeah. I can see that.
