Dialogue: 0.0:11:16.54.0:11:18.44.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(208.413)}I'm sitting here with both
Dialogue: 0.0:11:18.51.0:11:20.17.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(244.371)}of my legs broken.
Dialogue: 0.0:11:18.51.0:11:20.17.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(200.413)}and you're still asking me
