Dialogue: 0.0:11:21.84.0:11:23.33.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(275.410)}Ooh! Ow! Oh!
Dialogue: 0.0:11:23.41.0:11:24.67.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(223.413)}Y-y-you're a monster.
Dialogue: 0.0:11:24.75.0:11:26.48.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(203.413)}Y-you're like Hitler. but --
Dialogue: 0.0:11:26.55.0:11:28.57.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(189.368)}but even Hitler cared about
Dialogue: 0.0:11:26.55.0:11:28.57.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(212.413)}Germany or something.
Dialogue: 0.0:11:28.65.0:11:30.31.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(181.371)}Okay. hold on just a second.
Dialogue: 0.0:11:28.65.0:11:30.31.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(324.413)}Morty.
Dialogue: 0.0:11:30.39.0:11:33.69.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(291.413)}[groaning ]
Dialogue: 0.0:11:33.76.0:11:37.66.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(299.413)}[ panting ]
Dialogue: 0.0:11:37.73.0:11:41.72.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(331.410)}Ooh.
Dialogue: 0.0:11:41.80.0:11:45.39.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(331.410)}Ohh.
Dialogue: 0.0:11:49.77.0:11:51.47.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(331.410)}Ooh.
Dialogue: 0.0:11:52.51.0:11:53.70.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(289.412)}Wow. Rick.
Dialogue: 0.0:11:53.78.0:11:56.27.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(227.371)}That stuff just healed
Dialogue: 0.0:11:53.78.0:11:56.27.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(204.413)}my broken legs instantly.
Dialogue: 0.0:11:56.34.0:11:59.58.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(226.370)}I mean. I've never felt
Dialogue: 0.0:11:56.34.0:11:59.58.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(246.413)}so good in my life.
Dialogue: 0.0:11:59.65.0:12:00.58.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(289.413)}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0.0:12:00.65.0:12:01.91.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(192.413)}Don't worry about it. Morty.
Dialogue: 0.0:12:01.98.0:12:03.85.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(178.371)}Just come help me get these
Dialogue: 0.0:12:01.98.0:12:03.85.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(214.413)}seeds. all right. buddy?
Dialogue: 0.0:12:03.92.0:12:05.11.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(257.413)}Sure thing. Rick.
Dialogue: 0.0:12:05.19.0:12:06.68.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(196.371)}Not that you asked. Morty.
Dialogue: 0.0:12:05.19.0:12:06.68.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(213.413)}but what just happened
Dialogue: 0.0:12:06.75.0:12:09.66.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(191.368)}there is I went into a future
Dialogue: 0.0:12:06.75.0:12:09.66.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(166.410)}dimension with such advanced
Dialogue: 0.0:12:09.72.0:12:11.96.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(217.371)}medicine that they had
Dialogue: 0.0:12:09.72.0:12:11.96.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(195.413)}broken-leg serum at every
Dialogue: 0.0:12:12.03.0:12:13.32.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(252.413)}corner drugstore.
Dialogue: 0.0:12:13.39.0:12:14.59.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(225.368)}The stuff was all over
Dialogue: 0.0:12:13.39.0:12:14.59.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(254.413)}the place. Morty.
Dialogue: 0.0:12:14.66.0:12:16.15.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(168.413)}Wow. that's pretty crazy. Rick.
Dialogue: 0.0:12:16.23.0:12:17.60.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(199.371)}There's just one problem.
Dialogue: 0.0:12:16.23.0:12:17.60.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(314.413)}Morty --
Dialogue: 0.0:12:17.67.0:12:18.79.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(247.413)}one little hang-up.
Dialogue: 0.0:12:18.87.0:12:20.49.Dialogue2.Unknown.0000.0000.0000..{\an4\pos(165.368)}The dimension I visited was so
